                                <h3 class="h5 fw-bold mb-1" style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.2rem !important;">
                                    Divya & Parth</h3>
                                <p class="small mb-0" style="color: #6B21A8; font-weight: 500;">Grade 12,
                                    Mumbai</p>
