                            helping local farmers reduce manual labour applying STEM to problem-solving."
                        </p>
                        <div class="pt-3 border-top" style="border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb !important;">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                <span class="fw-bold" style="font-weight: 600;">Agri-Tech</span>
                                <span class="small text-secondary" style="color: #6B7280;">Market-Live Product</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Story 6 -->
                <div class="story-card snap-center">
                    <div class="story-image">
                        <img src="assets/slider/Pushpak.png" alt="Student presenting to audience" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start mb-3">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="h5 fw-bold mb-1" style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.2rem !important;">
                                    Pushpak, Tanuja & Utkarsha</h3>
                                <p class="small mb-0" style="color: #6B21A8; font-weight: 500;">Grade 10,
                                    Maharashtra</p>
                            </div>
                            <span class="story-badge">Ethical Sourcing</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-secondary fst-italic mb-4" style="color: #4B5563; font-size: 0.9rem !important;">
                            "Empowered by an entrepreneurial mindset, Pushpak, Tanuja & Utkarsha have built a
                            profit-generating FSSAI-certified spice brand turning adversity into opportunity, creating
                            livelihood for many."
                        </p>
                        <div class="pt-3 border-top" style="border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb !important;">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                <span class="fw-bold" style="font-weight: 600;">Agri-Supply Chain</span>
                                <span class="small text-secondary" style="color: #6B7280;">Market-Live Product</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
