                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ENpower Philosophy Section -->
    <section class="enpower-section">
        <div class="enpower-wrapper">
            <div class="enpower-container">
                <div class="enpower-left-content">
                    <!-- <div class="tag">ENpower Framework</div> -->
                    <h2>The ENpower <span>Philosophy</span></h2>
                    <div class="desc">
                        <p>The future of work is evolving faster than education systems can adapt. While global
                            frameworks like OECD, WEF, UNICEF, and India's NEP 2020 stress future skills, most schools
                            still focus on isolated STEM programs. </p>
                        <p>ENpower bridges this gap through a holistic future-skills ecosystem for schools. Built on 17
                            essential skills and 5 future-ready outcomes, it enables students to move from learning
                            concepts to solving real-world problems and becoming confident future leaders.</p>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#" class="cta-btn">Learn More</a>
                </div>

                <div class="enpower-right-cards">
                    <div class="enpower-radial-wrap" id="enpowerRadialWrap">
                        <svg id="enpower-radial-svg" viewBox="0 0 520 520" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <defs>
                                <radialGradient id="enpowerCGrad" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
                                    <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#ffffff" />
                                    <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#f0ede6" />
                                </radialGradient>
                                <filter id="enpowerSoftShadow" x="-20%" y="-20%" width="140%" height="140%">
                                    <feDropShadow dx="0" dy="3" stdDeviation="8" flood-color="rgba(0,0,0,0.12)" />
                                </filter>
                            </defs>
                            <g id="enpowerSegGroup"></g>
                            <!-- Center -->
                            <circle cx="260" cy="260" r="82" class="enpower-center-bg" fill="url(#enpowerCGrad)"
                                filter="url(#enpowerSoftShadow)" />
                            <circle cx="260" cy="260" r="88" class="enpower-center-ring" />
                            <text x="260" y="246" class="enpower-ct-label">Pillar</text>
                            <text x="260" y="274" class="enpower-ct-num" id="enpowerCtNum">—</text>
                            <text x="260" y="293" class="enpower-ct-sub" id="enpowerCtSub">Scroll</text>
                        </svg>
                        <div class="enpower-info-card" id="enpowerInfoCard"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="enpower-scroll-progress">
                    <div class="enpower-progress-track">
                        <div class="enpower-progress-fill"></div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="enpower-progress-label">Scroll to explore</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
